HEADWORD: Stylagalmaic
<hw>Sty`la*gal*ma"ic</hw>
<pr>(st⟦imac⟧`l⟦adot⟧*g⟦acr⟧l*m⟦amac⟧"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[Gr. <grk>sty^los</grk> a column + <grk>'a`galma</grk> an
image.]</ety> <fld>(Arch.)</fld> <def>Performing the office of columns;
<as>as, Atlantes and Caryatides are <ex>stylagalmaic</ex> figures or
images</as>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>stylogalmaic</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
